Insider Activity


Individual




Bruce H. Besanko



Mr. Bruce H. Besanko is EVP, Chief Operating & Financial Officer at SUPERVALU, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at USO of Illinois. Mr. Besanko was previously employed as EVP, Chief Financial & Administrative Officer by OfficeMax, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Circuit City Stores, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President by The Yankee Candle Co., Inc., and Vice President-Finance by Best Buy Co., Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Cincinnati (Ohio) and an MBA from The University of Chicago.



